snippet.title: Smash and Bash Monsters - DEMO Trailer
snippet.description:
An addicting "Clicker-Looter" game where you defeat Thousands of monsters to loot equipment and get stronger, that can be as Relaxing or Frenetic as you like!

Download the the demo at https://dugringo.itch.io/smash-and-bash-monsters
Wishlist on Steam at https://store.steampowered.com/app/2681260/Smash_and_Bash_Monsters/

Attention, this video contains Pre-Alpha footage and everything is subject to change! 

Thank you!
